# ============================================
# Think ABC - Environment Variables
# ============================================

# ============================================
# AI Provider API Keys (Backend - Set in Vercel)
# ============================================

# IMPORTANT: These keys should be set in Vercel Environment Variables
# NOT in .env.local (they are used by backend API, not frontend)

# REQUIRED: Google Gemini API Key
# Gemini is used because it can analyze AUDIO files directly (transcribe + analyze in one step)
# Get your FREE API key at: https://makersuite.google.com/app/apikey
# GEMINI_API_KEY=your_gemini_api_key_here

# Note: All AI calls now go through /api/analyze-call backend endpoint
# This makes it bulletproof with proper error handling and graceful fallbacks

# ============================================
# Supabase Configuration (For Audio Storage)
# ============================================

# RECOMMENDED: Supabase for unlimited audio file storage
# Without Supabase, audio files are limited to 3MB (falls back to base64)
# With Supabase, you can upload audio files of any size (100MB+)

# Get these from: https://app.supabase.com/project/_/settings/api
# VITE_SUPABASE_URL=https://your-project.supabase.co
# VITE_SUPABASE_ANON_KEY=your_anon_key_here

# After setting up Supabase:
# 1. Create a new bucket called "CALL_RECORDINGS"
# 2. Set it to PUBLIC (or use RLS policies)
# 3. Enable CORS for your domain

# Optional: Super Admin Credentials
# VITE_SUPER_ADMIN_EMAIL=admin@thinkabc.com
# VITE_SUPER_ADMIN_PASSWORD=YourSecurePassword123!

# Optional: Analytics & Tracking
# VITE_GOOGLE_ANALYTICS_ID=G-XXXXXXXXXX
# VITE_MIXPANEL_TOKEN=your_mixpanel_token_here

# Optional: Feature Flags
# VITE_ENABLE_VOICE_ROLEPLAY=true
# VITE_ENABLE_CALL_RECORDING=true
# VITE_ENABLE_MARKET_INTEL=true

# Optional: API Endpoints (if using custom backend)
# VITE_API_BASE_URL=https://api.thinkabc.app
# VITE_WEBSOCKET_URL=wss://ws.thinkabc.app

# Optional: Sentry Error Tracking
# VITE_SENTRY_DSN=https://xxx@xxx.ingest.sentry.io/xxx

# Optional: Authentication (for future use)
# VITE_AUTH0_DOMAIN=your-domain.auth0.com
# VITE_AUTH0_CLIENT_ID=your_client_id_here

# ============================================
# Email Configuration (Vercel Environment Variables Only)
# Note: These should be set in Vercel Dashboard, NOT in .env.local
# ============================================

# Required for Email Sending (Set in Vercel)
# Get your API key from: https://resend.com/api-keys
# RESEND_API_KEY=re_xxxxxxxxxxxx

# Email Settings (Set in Vercel)
# SENDER_EMAIL=Think ABC <noreply@thinkalm.ai>
# ADMIN_EMAIL=charlie@thinkalm.ai

# ============================================
# Instructions:
# 1. Copy this file to .env.local
# 2. Replace placeholder values with your actual keys
# 3. Never commit .env.local to version control
# 4. Required: VITE_GEMINI_API_KEY (app won't work without it)
# 5. Email vars (RESEND_API_KEY, SENDER_EMAIL, ADMIN_EMAIL) should be set
#    in Vercel Dashboard → Settings → Environment Variables
# ============================================
